\title "Sasha Alex Sloan - Dancing With Your Ghost"
\artist "Sasha Alex Sloan"
\track "Guitar" { instrument "Acoustic Guitar Steel" }
\staff {score tabs}
\lyrics "Yellin' at the sky, screamin' at the world Baby, why'd you go away, I'm still your girl? Holdin' on too tight, head up in the clouds Heaven only knows where you are now  How do I love? How do I love again? How do I trust? How do I trust again?  I stay up all night, tell myself I'm alright Baby, you're just harder to see than most I put the record on, wait 'til I hear our song Every night I'm dancing with your ghost Every night I'm dancing with your ghost  Never got the chance To say a last goodbye I gotta move on But it hurts to try  How do I love? How do I love again? How do I trust? How do I trust again?  I stay up all night, tell myself I'm alright Baby, you're just harder to see than most I put the record on, wait 'til I hear our song Every night I'm dancing with your ghost Every night I'm dancing with your ghost  How do I love? How do I love again? How do I trust? How do I trust again?  I stay up all night, tell myself I'm alright Baby, you're just harder to see than most I put the record on, wait 'til I hear our song Every night I'm dancing with your ghost Every night I'm dancing with your ghost  Every night I'm dancing with your ghost"
\ts (4 4)
\tuning (E4 B3 G3 D3 A2 E2)
